<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>Страница регистрации нового сотрудника</title>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css"/>
</head>
<body>
<center><h1>Регистрация нового сотрудника</h1></center>
<form action="/registration" method="post">
    <center>
        <br class="row g-3">

        <center><div class="form-floating mb-3 w-25">
            <input type="text" name="username" value="{{#username}}{{username}}{{/username}}" class="form-control"
                   id="floatingInput" placeholder="Username">
            <label for="floatingInput">Username</label>
        </div></center>

        <center><div class="form-floating w-25">
            <input type="password" name="password" value="{{#password}}{{password}}{{/password}}"
                   class="form-control" id="floatingPassword" placeholder="Password">
            <label for="floatingPassword">Password</label>
        </div></center>
        <div><input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{_csrf.token}}"></div>
        {{#found_userfromDB}}
            Пользователь с таким именем уже существует!
        {{/found_userfromDB}}
        {{^found_userfromDB}}{{/found_userfromDB}}
        <br/><br/>
        <div><input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" value="Зарегистрироваться"/></div>
        </div>
    </center>
</form>
<center><div style="margin-top:20px;"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/login" role="button">Вернуться на страницу авторизации</a></div></center>
</body>
</html>